Definition: of a body of water) free from disturbance by heavy waves
Example: a ribbon of sand between the angry sea and the placid bay; the quiet waters of a lagoon; a lake of tranquil blue water reflecting a tranquil blue sky; a smooth channel crossing; scarcely a ripple on the still water; unruffled water
Synonyms: noun, feeling, placidness, quiet, quietness, still, state, stillness, tranquil, tranquility, tranquillity, smooth, attribute, smoothness, unruffled, of, a, body, water, free, from, disturbance, by, heavy, waves, ribbon, sand, between, the, angry, sea, and, bay, waters, lagoon, lake, blue, reflecting, sky, channel, crossing, scarcely, ripple, on
Category: adj.all
